data.description: Serene and peaceful 1.5 story located at Woodland Lake Estates w/ association owned lake. Bondurant schools, paved roads, fantastic location! This adorable 4 bedroom 3 bath home is uniquely designed to provide beautiful design and functionality. Walking in your will be wowed by the floor to ceiling slider windows that open up to the private backyard. This home is move-in ready with updates throughout including remodeled kitchen, new trim and paint inside and out, new windows, new roof, and many more.  The basement is perfect for entertaining with lots of room with a new wet bar and 2nd gas fireplace.  Need garage space? Attached 4+ car heated garage should do the trick. Enjoy the outdoors and country living with amazing views from inside the house, or sit on the large wrap around main level partially covered deck looking out into the fully fenced in yard. A bonus second deck is accessible from the master bedroom.  All information obtained from seller and public records.
